            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/gradient-generator/">Gradient Generator</a> — Create beautiful CSS gradients 
              for backgrounds and visual accents.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Every tool runs entirely in your browser. No uploads. No tracking. Just fast, reliable 
            color utilities that respect your privacy.
          </p>
        </section>

